					</div>
					<div class="project-card">
						<div class="project-icon">ü§ñ</div>
						<h3>Ninja AI Chat</h3>
						<p>LLM Streaming & Multi-Model AI</p>
						<a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ninja-ai-chat-code-create/id6702030312" target="_blank" class="project-link">View on App Store ‚Üí</a>
